The name Lasta first appeared as a company when it was formed by the Yugoslav government in February 1947. The company's first day of operation was on April 1, 1947.Lasta - O nama Istorijat - 1945-2000 Only in 2006 did Lasta begin city transit operations in Belgrade to compliment its intercity services.Lasta - O nama - Istorijat - Od 2000 do danas (Serbian)